cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for estimating human pose from images and videos. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training a neural network, which falls under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves using unsupervised techniques to obtain coarse pose estimation, which falls under the sub-category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves analyzing videos, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves using pose estimation for action recognition, which falls under the sub-category cs.RO (Robotics).
